

POST Request Timeline:

T=0ms    npm run test:home (sends 1-0)
         ↓
T=1ms    API: Updates Redis cache instantly
         API: LPUSH message to score_updates list
         Redis list now has: [{"matchId":1, "score_home":1, ...}]
         
T=2ms    API: Returns 200 OK to user (user doesn't wait!)
         
         [Meanwhile, in background]
         
T=50ms   Worker: BRPOP detects message
         Redis list still has: [{"matchId":1, "score_home":1, ...}]
         
T=51ms   Worker: Parses JSON
         Worker: UPDATE database
         
T=52ms   Worker: BRPOP message (removes it)
